<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 13:22:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>科学家研究了癌症如何扩散。然后他们发现了一个意想不到的盟友</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-studied-how-cancer-spreads-then-they-found-an-unexpected-ally</link><description>隐藏的血管细胞可能会影响免疫反应，指出了研究人员正在竞相探索的一个令人惊讶的目标。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-studied-how-cancer-spreads-then-they-found-an-unexpected-ally.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 13:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-studied-how-cancer-spreads-then-they-found-an-unexpected-ally</guid></item><item><title>条纹还是格子？磁场影响类石墨烯量子材料中的竞争电子模式</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/striped-or-checkered-magnetic-field-influences-competing-electronic-patterns-in-a-graphene-like-quantum-material</link><description>在大多数日常材料中，例如铜、银和硅，电子的行为是相对可预测的。然而，在量子材料中，电子可以以复杂的方式相互作用，产生具有显着特性的集体电子态。了解这些状态如何出现以及最终如何控制它们是量子材料研究的核心挑战之一。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/striped-or-checkered-magnetic-field-influences-competing-electronic-patterns-in-a-graphene-like-quantum-material.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 13:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/striped-or-checkered-magnetic-field-influences-competing-electronic-patterns-in-a-graphene-like-quantum-material</guid></item><item><title>肥胖衍生代谢物调节肿瘤微环境中的抗肿瘤免疫：从机制到临床应用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/obesity-derived-metabolites-modulate-anti-tumor-immunity-in-the-tumor-microenvironment-from-mechanisms-to-clinical-applications</link><description>肿瘤微环境（TME）越来越多地被理解为一个代谢动态生态系统，其中局部代谢物的可用性、组成和运输塑造了免疫细胞的适应性和治疗反应性。在全球肥胖流行的背景下，肥胖相关的全身代谢失调与肿瘤的发生和进展有关，也可能影响肿瘤的免疫环境和治疗反应。本综述探讨了肥胖衍生的全身代谢物如何调节抗肿瘤免疫并影响癌症免疫治疗，特别强调代谢重编程和 TME 重塑所涉及的途径。我们进一步讨论了干预策略，涵盖（i）上游代谢物生成，（ii）系统到局部转运到 TME，以及（iii）TME 内的直接功能拮抗。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/obesity-derived-metabolites-modulate-anti-tumor-immunity-in-the-tumor-microenvironment-from-mechanisms-to-clinical-applications2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 12:52:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/obesity-derived-metabolites-modulate-anti-tumor-immunity-in-the-tumor-microenvironment-from-mechanisms-to-clinical-applications</guid></item><item><title>这是宇宙中最大的恒星之一。科学家称它看起来即将爆炸</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/this-is-one-of-the-biggest-stars-in-the-universe-scientists-say-it-looks-like-its-about-to-explode</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 12:37:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/this-is-one-of-the-biggest-stars-in-the-universe-scientists-say-it-looks-like-its-about-to-explode</guid></item><item><title>令人惊讶的证据我们的宇宙位于黑洞内部</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-surprising-evidence-our-universe-is-inside-a-black-hole</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 12:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-surprising-evidence-our-universe-is-inside-a-black-hole</guid></item><item><title>三种基因修饰剂可能会改变遗传性阿尔茨海默病的发病和进展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/three-genetic-modifiers-may-alter-inherited-alzheimers-onset-and-progression</link><description>常染色体显性阿尔茨海默病 (ADAD) 是一种遗传性阿尔茨海默病，仅占阿尔茨海默病病例的 1% 左右。然而，由于携带该基因突变的个体极有可能在幼年时患上阿尔茨海默病，而且该突变具有高度遗传性，因此阿尔茨海默病研究人员广泛研究了 ADAD。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/three-genetic-modifiers-may-alter-inherited-alzheimers-onset-and-progression2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 12:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/three-genetic-modifiers-may-alter-inherited-alzheimers-onset-and-progression</guid></item><item><title>SAXON Q 推出商用钻石 NV-Center 量子计算系统</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/saxon-q-launches-commercial-diamond-based-nv-center-quantum-computing-systems</link><description>SAXON Q 推出商用基于金刚石的 NV 中心量子计算机，提供专为研究和工业工作负载设计的室温系统。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/saxon-q-launches-commercial-diamond-based-nv-center-quantum-computing-systems.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 11:52:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/saxon-q-launches-commercial-diamond-based-nv-center-quantum-computing-systems</guid></item><item><title>创建健康跨度数字孪生：人类生活更美好的新时代 — 7 月 30 日</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/creating-a-healthspan-digital-twin-a-new-era-for-humanity-to-better-living-jul-30</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 11:37:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/creating-a-healthspan-digital-twin-a-new-era-for-humanity-to-better-living-jul-30</guid></item><item><title>流氓DNA可以从一个细胞移动到另一个细胞并改变它们的功能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/rogue-dna-can-move-from-cell-to-cell-and-change-how-they-function</link><description>OMRF 教授兼研究合著者加里·戈尔布斯基 (Gary Gorbsky) 表示：“我们在二维培养物中观察这一现象，但在实际的人体组织中，细胞紧密地堆积在一起，你可能会预料到这种情况会更频繁地发生。” “这开启了信息遗传转移新过程的可能性。” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/rogue-dna-can-move-from-cell-to-cell-and-change-how-they-function.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 11:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/rogue-dna-can-move-from-cell-to-cell-and-change-how-they-function</guid></item><item><title>初创公司创始人敦促特朗普不要关闭中国开放重量级人工智能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/startup-founders-urge-trump-not-to-shut-off-chinese-open-weight-ai</link><description>包括 Proton 和 Y Combinator 在内的近 200 家硅谷公司敦促特朗普政府不要切断对中国开放权重人工智能模型的访问，否则可能会导致下一代美国初创企业陷入瘫痪。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/startup-founders-urge-trump-not-to-shut-off-chinese-open-weight-ai.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 11:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/startup-founders-urge-trump-not-to-shut-off-chinese-open-weight-ai</guid></item></channel></rss>